**For First-Year Students Who Are Intermediate in Coding & Want AI/ML Future**

Hello bro!  
You are in **first year B.Tech CSE / AIML** — but your level is already **intermediate**.  
That means you are **much ahead** of most first-year students.  
Most are still learning basic Python or C++. You already know good Python, solved many problems, maybe built some projects.  

