## Phase 0 – Mindset + Setup (First 30–60 Days)

### 1. Simple Mindset
- You are early — enjoy it
- Daily small work > big weekend study
- College marks important — don’t drop below 7.5 CGPA
- Mistakes = learning — don’t fear them
- Balance: code + friends + rest + college
- One good problem + one project step + one application = win

### 2. Easy Tracking
Use one Google Sheet or Notion page:

